            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-3-1678455854627-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-3-1678455854627-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Combine your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>red chilli relish</strong> and the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s]</strong> – this is your <strong>sweet chilli dip</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-copy-3-1678455857820-x200.jpg",
