          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-copy-3-1678455857820-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-style pork & prawn cakes </strong>with the <strong>ginger pak choi</strong>, <strong>coconut rice </strong>and<strong> sweet chilli dip </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining coriander leaves</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
